Package ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddDestinationActivity
    Used for adding and editing destinations.
    AddTagToClaimActivity
    Activity to add tags to an existing claim.
    ExpenseClaimActivity
    Activity that handles the creation of new ExpenseClaims and the editing of existing ExpenseClaims.
    ExpenseClaimListActivity
    Displays a list of claims available to the user, providing summary details.
    ExpenseItemActivity
    Allows a user to edit a new or existing expense item.
    ExpenseItemDetailActivity
    Activity that lets the user view information of the selected ExpenseItem Used when an expense item is selected from the ExpenseItemListFragment Covers Issue 16
    GeolocationViewActivity
    Activity responsible for getting a geolocation coordinate.
    LoginAsApproverOrClaimantActivity
    Activity for choosing between a Claimant and Approver UI.
    ManageTagActivity
    Activity that handles viewing all the tags.
    MapViewActivity
    This Activity lets Claimant set on a map by putting a marker.
    ReceiptViewActivity
    View receipt of an Expense Item.
    RemoveTagFromClaimActivity
    Activity for removing tags from an existing claim.
    TabbedSummaryActivity
    Superclass activity for the tabbed summary views.
    TabbedSummaryApproverActivity
    Creates Approver specific menu items (Approve Claim, Return Claim and Comment) in the tabbedSummaryActivity
    TabbedSummaryClaimantActivity
    Deals with displaying the ClaimSummaryFragment, ExpenseItemListFragment, and DestinationListFragment.
    ViewCommentsActivity
    Displays a list of all comments associated with a given claim.
